Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.94,0:02:15.57,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,就用这颗子弹破坏一切！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.57,0:02:20.74,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,NEVER LIE 即使在这仅剩黑白 暗无光辉的世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:25.66,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,NEVER END NEVER LIE 心灵绝不沾染黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.66,0:02:31.50,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,THE END OF WORLD 在绝望中握住仅存的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.50,0:02:40.43,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,用颤抖的手指瞄准目标 去追寻未来！
Comment: 0,0:22:26.19,0:22:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,——————————————EDJP——————————————
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.45,0:22:26.66,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}終わりが始まるアリアと共に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.66,0:22:31.33,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}白旗を掲げた奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.83,0:22:37.09,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}脱獄の果てに歓声の中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.09,0:22:41.26,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}手錠突き付けられ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.72,0:22:47.14,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}ほら、見て　愚かな駒よ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.14,0:22:52.19,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}断罪の茶番
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.27,0:22:54.94,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}独壇場Funky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.94,0:22:57.61,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}その目で見ろ　競争
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.66,0:23:02.70,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}Forget
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.61,0:23:02.70,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}欺いてよ　Close Enough
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.70,0:23:05.28,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}多発的な展開
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.28,0:23:08.08,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人の波を掻き分け
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.08,0:23:10.79,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}叫べ　My Justice，Right Way
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.79,0:23:13.17,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Make it a vow!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.17,0:23:15.79,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感心できるのはFunky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.79,0:23:18.51,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喪失だけが拒止
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.51,0:23:23.51,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}導いてよ　Close Enough
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.55,0:23:26.18,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}鮮烈過ぎた年回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.26,0:23:28.35,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}偏見のあるカテゴライズ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.35,0:23:30.56,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Don't believe no story
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.56,0:23:32.60,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}I know you're ready
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.60,0:23:34.48,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}No, we're already over
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.48,0:23:36.48,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Everybody loves despair
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.48,0:23:39.90,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}I'll sadly go from the end
Comment: 0,0:22:16.19,0:22:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,——————————————EDCN——————————————
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.45,0:22:26.66,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}伴随着结尾即开始的咏叹调
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.66,0:22:31.33,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}高举白旗的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.83,0:22:37.09,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在逃狱后的欢呼声中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.09,0:22:41.26,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被强行拷上了手铐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.72,0:22:47.14,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看吧 愚昧的棋子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.14,0:22:52.19,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这定罪的把戏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.27,0:22:54.94,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}奇异的独角戏舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.94,0:22:57.61,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}用你的眼睛看着 竞争
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.66,0:23:02.70,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}遗落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.61,0:23:02.70,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}欺骗吧 Close Enough
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.70,0:23:05.28,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}多线并行的发展
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.28,0:23:08.08,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拨开人群
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.08,0:23:10.79,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呼喊着 这是我正义的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.79,0:23:13.17,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}许下你的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.17,0:23:15.79,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}值得赞美的惊恐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.79,0:23:18.51,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}唯独拒绝丧失
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.51,0:23:23.51,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}指引我吧 Close Enough
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.55,0:23:26.18,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}过于艳丽的忌日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.26,0:23:28.35,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}带有偏见的分类
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.35,0:23:30.56,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要相信没有故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.56,0:23:32.60,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道你准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.60,0:23:34.48,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 我们已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.48,0:23:36.48,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人人都爱着绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.48,0:23:39.90,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我会满怀悲伤地离去
